<h1 class="no_toc fs-9" id="aria">ARIA</h1>

<p class="fs-6 fw-300">Accessible Rich Internet Applications (ARIA) allow web developers to make web content more accessible to people with disabilities and other limitations.</p>

<hr />

<h2 class="no_toc text-delta" id="table-of-contents">Table of contents</h2>

<ol id="markdown-toc">
